305
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:59,452
- Come on, go to bed.
- Come on, say it.

306
00:32:01,294 --> 00:32:03,126
I love you.

307
00:32:03,797 --> 00:32:05,458
I love you, too.

308
00:32:08,301 --> 00:32:09,837
You've got a cat?

309
00:32:16,810 --> 00:32:19,677
Go get us some water, I'm thirsty.
Come on.

310
00:32:20,647 --> 00:32:22,137
Come on.

311
00:32:29,531 --> 00:32:32,319
Well, I guess I know my place.

312
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:36,027
