313
00:32:36,872 --> 00:32:40,536
"Get me water, bake me a cake"...
What happened to "please"?

314
00:33:28,089 --> 00:33:30,922
Good boy, Sackface. Go for a walk.

315
00:33:40,352 --> 00:33:43,219
- Let her go.
- Cut her throat, man.

316
00:33:45,941 --> 00:33:48,899
- What did you say?
- Cut her fucking throat.

317
