326
00:34:36,157 --> 00:34:37,739
Lose the mask.

327
00:34:41,121 --> 00:34:42,611
Relax, have a smoke. You smoke?

328
00:34:46,293 --> 00:34:48,785
Whose idea was this? Who sent you?

329
00:34:49,546 --> 00:34:51,628
