335
00:35:27,500 --> 00:35:29,992
You pig! You sick fuck!

336
00:35:32,172 --> 00:35:35,790
You wanted gambling. That's gambling.
Call the police.

337
00:35:40,722 --> 00:35:44,090
- You killed the other guy too?
- He went for my gun.

338
00:35:44,893 --> 00:35:48,102
It was self-defense.
Go ahead, call the police.

339
00:35:49,272 --> 00:35:51,309
- No, no...
- I'm taking pictures.

340
00:35:51,399 --> 00:35:53,015
No pictures.

341
00:35:54,903 --> 00:35:56,143
<i>You had a gun!</i>

342
00:35:56,571 --> 00:36:01,407
They only had a knife. You could have
handed them over to the police.

343
00:36:02,327 --> 00:36:05,490
Zasa sent them.
I just sent him a message.

344
00:36:06,581 --> 00:36:11,747
- Now he has to send you one back.
- Zasa is going to send me one back?

345
00:36:11,836 --> 00:36:14,749
He did the right thing.
He got Zasa's name!

346
00:36:14,839 --> 00:36:18,582
What has Joey Zasa to do
with anything? Joey Zasa is a <i>pazzo.</i>

347
00:36:22,263 --> 00:36:24,800
All right. You are what you are.

348
00:36:25,433 --> 00:36:28,266
It's your nature. Stay close to me.

349
00:36:28,353 --> 00:36:32,187
Don't do anything.
Keep your mouth shut and your eyes open.

350
00:36:32,691 --> 00:36:35,524
- And you do what I tell you.
- I understand.

351
00:36:35,610 --> 00:36:38,978
- I have problems with the Commission.
- I know.

352
00:36:39,072 --> 00:36:43,737
- You don't make them easier.
