353
00:36:44,744 --> 00:36:47,281
- Get out of here.
- Michael...

354
00:36:47,831 --> 00:36:49,071
Yes?

355
00:36:50,917 --> 00:36:54,581
- Now they'll fear you.
- Maybe they should fear <i>you.</i>

356
00:36:58,508 --> 00:37:02,342
- B.J., what's up?
