357
00:37:02,429 --> 00:37:05,296
We've arranged some amazing things.

358
00:37:05,390 --> 00:37:09,349
The publicity is phenomenal. You're
the new Rockefeller. A philanthropist.

359
00:37:11,855 --> 00:37:15,098
- Sigh here, please.
- Times do change, don't they?

360
00:37:15,775 --> 00:37:20,315
My father hated foundations.
He loved doing it by himself.

361
00:37:21,489 --> 00:37:24,026
Man to man. But we're different.

362
00:37:24,117 --> 00:37:29,612
No different than any large corporation.
We control a lot of money with little.

363
00:37:29,706 --> 00:37:34,121
Minimize taxes.
With no government control.

364
00:37:43,052 --> 00:37:45,965
- Godfather.
- Andrew.

365
00:37:48,183 --> 00:37:52,302
- Off to Rome...
- I wanted to thank you for everything.

366
00:37:52,854 --> 00:37:55,937
- Do you want some breakfast?
- Thanks, I can't.

367
00:37:56,524 --> 00:38:00,438
- How's your Italian?
- <i>Devo fare un po' di pratica.</i>

368
00:38:01,696 --> 00:38:03,983
- His father was a great lawyer.
- I know.

369
00:38:04,073 --> 00:38:07,486
Didn't live to see him ordained. I did.
Did you ever see one of those?

370
00:38:08,828 --> 00:38:12,321
Beautiful. I was so proud.
Let me walk you out.

371
00:38:13,750 --> 00:38:16,242
If you hear any rumors in the Vatican,
let me know.

372
00:38:16,336 --> 00:38:18,873
No, Andrew has the true faith.

373
00:38:21,508 --> 00:38:25,627
<i>The motion under discussion
relates to Corleone Group's proposal</i>

374
00:38:26,596 --> 00:38:31,557
<i>to acquire 100,000,000 newly issued
Class A voting shares.</i>

375
00:38:34,729 --> 00:38:39,644
<i>Corleone capital invested
directly in to International Immobfliere,</i>

376
00:38:40,610 --> 00:38:44,023
<i>an old and respected
European company.</i>

377
00:38:44,906 --> 00:38:47,773
Mr. Corleone has
an ambitious program

378
00:38:47,867 --> 00:38:50,450
to expand this real estate company

379
00:38:50,537 --> 00:38:53,529
into an international conglomerate...

380
00:38:56,584 --> 00:39:02,455
by Eastern techniques of efficiency
and focus and unlimited...

381
00:39:02,549 --> 00:39:04,586
Mr. Corleone, excuse me.

382
00:39:05,134 --> 00:39:08,672
Didn't you recently deposit 200 million
in the Vatican Bank,

383
00:39:08,763 --> 00:39:11,801
which is affiliated with Immobiliare?

