385
00:39:13,601 --> 00:39:20,143
Wasn't there any questioning about
the timing on this particular deposit?

386
00:39:20,233 --> 00:39:22,395
Mr. Chairman, if I may?

387
00:39:23,987 --> 00:39:28,697
The Vito Andolini Corleone Foundation,
of which Mary Corleone is chairman,

388
00:39:28,783 --> 00:39:31,992
has made an endowment
of 100 million dollars.

389
00:39:32,078 --> 00:39:36,572
The money comes from his own family
and will be administered by the Vatican.

390
00:39:36,666 --> 00:39:38,873
Does that answer your question?

391
00:39:39,377 --> 00:39:44,747
My fellow shareholders, if Europe
and America can learn to co-operate,

392
00:39:44,841 --> 00:39:49,176
if we can learn to pool our wealth,
share our markets,

393
00:39:49,262 --> 00:39:53,756
we can defeat any competition
anywhere in the world.

394
00:39:54,559 --> 00:39:57,176
Thank you for your time.

395
00:39:57,270 --> 00:40:01,889
I hope that you will look favorably
on my proposal. Thank you.

396
00:40:04,152 --> 00:40:07,270
Let me have this microphone here.

397
00:40:07,363 --> 00:40:12,449
Will we let a criminal run our company?
He's got the map of Sicily on his face!

398
00:40:12,535 --> 00:40:13,535
Order!

399
00:40:13,620 --> 00:40:16,157
He's either a Catholic or a mafioso...

400
00:40:17,707 --> 00:40:19,289
Mr. Chairman...

401
00:40:19,709 --> 00:40:24,875
the Vatican Bank feels
that International Immobiliare...

402
00:40:24,964 --> 00:40:29,003
will be safe in Mr. Corleone's hands.

403
00:40:29,928 --> 00:40:32,761
Subject to audit
and final ratification,

404
00:40:32,847 --> 00:40:34,838
which must take place in Rome.

405
00:40:34,933 --> 00:40:38,221
Please join me in welcoming
Mr. Michael Corleone.

406
00:40:46,653 --> 00:40:51,898
Mary! Mary, this is real.
This foundation is real.

407
00:40:54,702 --> 00:40:59,913
I wanted Anthony to be part of it.
I thought you would be together on this.

408
00:40:59,999 --> 00:41:04,493
I won't interfere.
I'll help, but only if you ask.

409
00:41:04,587 --> 00:41:06,578
What is this really for?

410
00:41:07,298 --> 00:41:10,711
Why are you doing this?
Why am I doing this?

411
00:41:12,303 --> 00:41:17,389
I'm doing this for my children.
You're doing it for your children too.

412
00:41:18,184 --> 00:41:21,097
This foundation is supposed to
help all people.

413
00:41:21,187 --> 00:41:22,769
That's the purpose.

414
00:41:23,856 --> 00:41:28,441
This is legitimate.
Mary, I swear, this is legitimate.

415
00:41:32,573 --> 00:41:35,531
Dad, I want this to bring me
closer to you.

416
00:41:44,127 --> 00:41:47,836
I would burn in hell to keep you safe.

417
00:42:01,853 --> 00:42:04,766
Go in the other car.
I'll ride with Michael.

418
00:42:05,148 --> 00:42:06,684
Go, go, go.

419
00:42:20,663 --> 00:42:25,499
Your old partners are grateful
for the money you made them.

420
00:42:25,585 --> 00:42:27,371
