on Immobiliare, to be a family again.

423
00:42:41,267 --> 00:42:43,884
It can purify their money.

424
00:42:46,189 --> 00:42:47,975
This I cannot do.

425
00:42:50,818 --> 00:42:53,606
Immobiliare must be legitimate.

426
00:42:56,199 --> 00:42:57,405
I know.

427
00:42:58,451 --> 00:43:00,488
But they're unhappy.

428
00:43:02,622 --> 00:43:03,953
And you?

429
00:43:04,791 --> 00:43:10,286
I ask nothing for myself.
Only peace in my old age.

430
00:43:10,838 --> 00:43:14,047
But I must please the world around me.

431
00:43:16,135 --> 00:43:22,051
Michael, your father was
a reasonable man. Learn from him.

432
00:43:24,560 --> 00:43:27,723
I learnt many things from my father.

433
00:43:33,402 --> 00:43:38,863
Call a meeting, my friend,
so there are no debts or grudges.

434
00:43:40,034 --> 00:43:42,867
