Group already controls the Board.

448
00:45:21,969 --> 00:45:26,588
According to the Lateran Treaty,
the Vatican vote must be ratified here.

449
00:45:26,682 --> 00:45:28,798
Here in Rome, by the Pope.

450
00:45:32,897 --> 00:45:36,015
The Pope is gravely ill.

451
00:45:37,485 --> 00:45:41,023
Until he recovers, I am powerless.

452
00:45:42,365 --> 00:45:45,027
- What if he dies?
- Then...

453
00:45:46,160 --> 00:45:49,243
as you Americans say,
all bets are off.

454
00:45:49,747 --> 00:45:51,658
Gentlemen, please.

455
00:45:53,084 --> 00:45:56,418
This is a brief delay. Nothing more.

456
00:46:01,509 --> 00:46:03,796
Your Excellency, gentlemen...

457
00:46:05,137 --> 00:46:10,348
I advise you to join us in our prayers
for the Holy Father's recovery.

458
00:46:11,727 --> 00:46:13,468
We had an agreement!

459
00:46:14,897 --> 00:46:18,606
This meeting was to be
merely a formality.

460
00:46:18,693 --> 00:46:24,029
- Please sit down.
- I'd rather stand. Give me an answer.

461
00:46:24,115 --> 00:46:29,610
The Immobiliare has its roots in the
European tradition. Please understand.

462
00:46:30,538 --> 00:46:33,906
I understand.
Your tactics are despicable.

463
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:37,118
That's quite an indictment,
coming from a Corleone.

464
00:46:37,211 --> 00:46:41,546
- Gentlemen, gentlemen!
- Remember you are in the Vatican.

465
00:46:45,469 --> 00:46:51,135
- What is it that you want?
- Yes, you will take control.

466
00:46:52,184 --> 00:46:55,643
